Renal replacement in end-stage renal disease patients over 75 years old.

Létourneau I(1), Ouimet D, Dumont M, Pichette V, Leblanc M.

Author information:
(1)Department of Nephrology, Maisonneuve-Rosemont Hospital, 5415 de 
l'Assomption, Montreal, P. Quebec, H1T 2M4, Canada.

BACKGROUND: Over the last decade, the age of dialysis patients has been 
